{
  "stem": "23438.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I went to Paris, and I got a job as proofreader in the Polish paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I rented a very small room in a very cheap hotel on the fifth floor, where it was freezing in winter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no heating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The central heating had broken down and nobody could repair it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, it was so hot in summer that I would open the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was not really a balcony, but a sort of a very narrow strip enclosed by a railing, and I just put my feet through that railing to have a bit of fresh air.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I worked as a proofreader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, after a while, I was asked to learn to work on a linotype, which was the print-setting machine then.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had no Polish-speaking printers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was very difficult for French-speaking or Jewish-speaking, Yiddish-speaking-- that was a Jewish print shop-- guys to work on the Polish texts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they taught me how the-- how the linotype works.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was doing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And one day, who walks into the print shop but Stefan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He never told me, never, 'til maybe 40 years later, that he didn't quite accidentally take that assignment to Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I thought he did, but he never quite admitted to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] here comes the story of my gold bracelet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When my mother was in the transit camp in Proszkow looking for me, walking around and asking people whether they have seen such and such a  girl, this woman that she'd never seen before came to her, took a thick gold chain from her hand, and gave it to my mother.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Take this, you may need some money to buy back your daughter from wherever she is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Total stranger.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
